Preheat oven to 375 degrees F (190 degrees C). Roast Garnet yams in oven until tender, 35 to 40 minutes. Cool slightly and cut into 1-inch chunks. Toss with O Organics(TM) Extra Virgin Olive Oil; add sherry wine vinegar, sea salt, and freshly ground black pepper (all to taste). Arrange on platter and sprinkle with chopped O Organics(TM) Mint leaves, sliced green onions, and crumbled goat cheese.